oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Advanced repro start-up
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Swenson, Ashley
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Advanced reproductive technologies (ART) and their respective services have been part of my repertoire since my childhood days. Flushing cows (in vivo collections) has been routinely per­formed on my family’s farm for decades. In more recent years, in vitro embryo production has become more prominently utilized by my farm as well as by my clients. Since purchasing Midwest Embryo Transfer Service in 2016, we have expanded the services offered to include: in vivo collections, ovum pick-up (OPU) for in vitro fertilization, fresh and frozen in vivo and in vitro embryo transfers, cryopreservation of both in vivo and in vitro embryos, and export services.
